GLESGAE - GL ES Game Application Engine

This is effectively an experimental engine by Steven "Stuckie" Campbell.
It's main aim is education of the various GL platforms, and providing a quick framework for throwing prototypes together.
It's not it's aim to provide a fully fledged engine environment ala Unity, Source or UDK.

Main platforms are Linux 32bit and 64bit.
Secondary platforms are Win32, Pandora, Android and iOS.
Tertiary platforms are OSX, GP2XWiz and Caanoo.
